sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS Reencrypt
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant Tekton as Tekton API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Storage as Minio/S3<br/>9000/TCP or 443/TCP
    participant TaskPod as Tekton TaskRun Pod
    participant PAgent as Persistence Agent
    participant MLMD as MLMD Envoy<br/>8080/TCP gRPC

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 1: User Submits Pipeline via API

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v1beta1/pipelines<br/>Auth: OAuth Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward HTTPS<br/>TLS Reencrypt
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OAuth Token<br/>OpenShift RBAC
    OAuth->>API: Forward HTTP/8888<br/>Verified Identity
    API->>DB: Store Pipeline Metadata<br/>MySQL + DB Password
    API->>Tekton: Create PipelineRun<br/>HTTPS + ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>OAuth: Pipeline Created Response
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution & Artifact Storage

    Tekton->>TaskPod: Start TaskRun Pod
    TaskPod->>Storage: Store Artifacts<br/>HTTP/HTTPS + S3 Access Keys
    Storage-->>TaskPod: Artifact Stored
    TaskPod->>Storage: Upload Model Output<br/>S3 API
    API->>Storage: Retrieve Artifacts<br/>S3 Credentials

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 3: Persistence Agent Status Sync

    PAgent->>Tekton: Watch PipelineRun Status<br/>HTTPS + ServiceAccount Token
    Tekton-->>PAgent: Status Update
    PAgent->>DB: Update Run Status<br/>MySQL + DB Password

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 4: MLMD Metadata Tracking

    API->>MLMD: Track Execution Metadata<br/>gRPC Internal
    MLMD->>DB: Store ML Metadata<br/>MySQL + DB Password

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 5: ODH Dashboard Integration

    User->>Route: GET /apis/v1beta1/pipelines<br/>Via Dashboard + OAuth
    Route->>OAuth: HTTPS TLS Reencrypt
    OAuth->>API: Forward HTTP/8888
    API->>DB: Fetch Pipeline List<br/>MySQL
    DB-->>API: Pipeline Data
    API-->>OAuth: JSON Response
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: Display in Dashboard
